Package com.example.goldencarrot.data.model.event

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.goldencarrot.data.model.event.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventConfigurator
public class Event extends Object implements EventConfigurator
The Event Class represents an Event stored in the system It stores the Organizer User Object that created the event This class provides implements methods to update and create Event Model Objects.
